Alas, I got around to finishing this map.

This is my first map I've made in a couple of months, I initially started it just to get back into mapping so hopefully it has indeed gotten me hooked on mapping once again.

This map is based more around fun / gameplay than visual appeal so please keep that in mind.

I apologize for no video, but my FRAPS is lagging the fuck out of me for some reason.

This was created for my clan KING. It's currently running at 208.167.232.72:27015 - Although it is a WC:S server.

If someone is willing to make a short video for me I'd GREATLY appreciate it, although I don't really have points to offer. ;P
